metadata.name: Star of Destruction
metadata.description:
The "Star of Destruction" in alchemy represents the process of destruction and decay, and is a necessary step in the transformation of matter. Terminatus was the first to destroy Prima Materia. To commemorate this achievement, I mark his Ethereum address with the "Star of Destruction." 
The branding of the "Star of Destruction" serves as a testament to Terminatus's bravery and achievement in the alchemic process.
